---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { SITE } from "../data/site";
---
<Base title="Shop — Coming Soon — Historical Translation Project™">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-14 sm:py-20">
    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/70 ring-1 ring-black/5 shadow-card p-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="font-display text-4xl text-ink">Shop — coming soon</div>
      <p class="mt-5 text-xl text-ink/75 leading-relaxed">
        We will enable Shopify checkout once manufacturing and fulfillment are ready.
        You’ll be able to purchase our formulations and vetted add‑on recommendations, pay securely, and route orders to our fulfillment partner.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-7 rounded-xl bg-parchment2 p-5 ring-1 ring-black/10">
        <div class="font-display text-2xl">Fulfillment center + Shopify</div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-ink/70 leading-relaxed">
          Even if a fulfillment center ships the products, Shopify is still typically used for checkout, taxes, customer emails,
          and pushing orders to the fulfillment partner automatically.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-7 rounded-xl bg-parchment2 p-5 ring-1 ring-black/10">
        <div class="font-display text-2xl">Get notified</div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-ink/70">Email us to be added to the launch list.</p>
        <a class="mt-4 inline-flex no-underline hover:no-underline rounded-md bg-gold text-ink font-semibold px-6 py-3 hover:bg-gold2 transition"
           href={`mailto:${SITE.email}?subject=HTP%20Shop%20Launch%20Updates&body=Please%20add%20me%20to%20the%20HTP%20shop%20launch%20list.`}>
          Notify me
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-ink/60">
        Educational content only; not medical advice. Supplements are not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent disease.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
